title: How to Install a K&N Air Intake on 2013-14 Honda Accord 3.5L
description: From start to finish, you'll see what's needed for installation of a K&N Air Intake (part # 69-1212TS).
tags: Install, Honda Accord, K&N Filter, K&N Intake

asset.title: 2013 and 2014 Honda Accord 3.5L K&N Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
The K&N 69-1212TS performance air intake system was designed for 2013 and 2014 Honda Accord models with a 3.5L engine. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-1212TS

This intake system created an estimated gain of 7.43 horsepower at 5,429 RPM and 8.62 lb. ft. of torque at 4,415 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. See how easy it is to add more performance to your car with this air intake system. 

http://www.knfilters.com
